nodes.text: Fidaval was a male Devaronian who was present at Tansarii Point Station around 1 ABY. He was the brother of Ratheb.

Fidaval appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
